highlights.text: “bad guy” by Billie Eilish is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #1.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 117 weeks straight.
Billie Eilish has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “bad guy” is the highest at #1.
“Contra La Pared” by Sean Paul and J Balvin is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 55 spots at #113.
